flowchart TD
    A([User Uploads Document\nPDF / Image / DOCX / TXT]) --> B{File Validation\nType and Size check}

    B -->|Invalid type or >20MB| ERR([HTTP 400 Error\nRejected])
    B -->|Valid| C[Save to uploads/]

    C --> D{File Type?}
    

    D -->|PDF| E[PyMuPDF\nRender each page\nat 300 DPI to PNG]
    D -->|PNG / JPG| F[PIL / Pillow\nLoad image as RGB]
    D -->|DOCX / DOC| G[python-docx\nExtract paragraphs\ndirectly - no OCR]
    D -->|TXT| H[UTF-8 decode\nNo processing needed]

    E --> PREP[Image Preprocessing\nOpenCV Pipeline]
    F --> PREP

    PREP --> P1[Grayscale\nconversion]
    P1 --> P2[Upscale if small\nINTER_CUBIC]
    P2 --> P3[fastNlMeans\nDenoising h=8]
    P3 --> P4[CLAHE\nclipLimit=2.0]
    P4 --> P5[Unsharp Mask\naddWeighted 1.5 / -0.5]

    P5 --> OCR

    subgraph OCRBOX [EasyOCR - two-stage deep learning, gpu=False]
        OCR[Stage 1 Detection\nCRAFT - CNN\nFinds where text is\nbounding boxes] --> REC1[Stage 2 Recognition\nCRNN reads each region]
        REC1 --> CNN[CNN - ResNet\nVisual features]
        CNN --> RNN[RNN - BiLSTM\nCharacter sequence + context]
        RNN --> CTC[CTC decoder\nFinal text + confidence]
    end

    G --> POST
    H --> SAVE

    CTC --> RAW[Keep regions conf > 0.3\nJoin into text lines]
    RAW --> POST[Post-Processing\nRegex corrections]

    POST --> FIX1[Fix currency symbol]
    POST --> FIX2[Fix O and l to 0 and 1 between digits]
    POST --> FIX3[Fix Rs and INR to currency symbol]
    POST --> FIX4[Fix email space dot]

    FIX1 & FIX2 & FIX3 & FIX4 --> CLEAN[Clean OCR text]

    CLEAN --> SAVE[Save to ocr_results]
    SAVE --> RESP[Return extracted_text\nto browser via JSON]

    RESP --> CHECK{Fields defined\nby user?}
    CHECK -->|No fields| RAWTAB[Show Raw Text tab]
    CHECK -->|Fields defined| EXT[POST /extract\nKeyword Proximity Search]

    EXT --> SCAN[Scan each OCR line\nagainst each field name]

    SCAN --> TIER1[Exact label match\nconf_base = 0.98]
    SCAN --> TIER2[Phrase in label / line\nconf_base = 0.95 / 0.90]
    SCAN --> TIER3[All field words match\nconf_base = 0.80]
    SCAN --> TIER4[60 percent words match\nconf_base = partial 0.40 to 0.68]

    TIER1 & TIER2 & TIER3 & TIER4 --> VAL[Extract value\nfrom same line after colon\nor next non-empty line]

    VAL --> CONF[Confidence adjustment\nSame line x1.0\nNext line x0.87\nNumeric fields prefer last match]

    CONF --> VALID{Validation\nFormat + Confidence}
    VALID --> VOK[Valid\nformat ok and conf >= 60]
    VALID --> VREV[Review\nformat ok but low confidence]
    VALID --> VINV[Invalid\nwrong format for field]
    VALID --> VMIS[Missing\nnot detected]

    VOK & VREV & VINV & VMIS --> OUT[Results JSON\nextractions overall_accuracy\nfields_found needs_review]

    OUT --> UI[UI Extracted Fields tab\nValue + confidence bars + validation badge\nGreen Valid - Amber Review - Red Invalid]

